:{{ProductPage|https://www.ampedwireless.com/ap600ex.html}}{{SupportPage|https://www.ampedwireless.com/ap600ex.html?support}} ([https://www.ampedwireless.com/media/datasheets/support/AP600EX_SetupGuide_LR.pdf Setup Guide], [https://www.ampedwireless.com/media/datasheets/support/AP600EX_UsersGuide_LR.pdf Users Guide], [https://www.ampedwireless.com/media/datasheets/Amped_AP600EX_Datasheet_LR.pdf Datasheet]) This is a Loopcomm device, the device uses the same hardware as the [[Amped Wireless SR600EX]] "LPC0033 REV:2.2" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. Per the manual, the default SSID is '''Amped_Pro_AP'''. The default WPA key is '''wireless'''. OUI may be or include F8:7B:8C.
